zo de la Serpiente]]'' (Colombia)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Ciro Guerra]]'''\n** ''[[The Clan (2015 film)|El Clan]]'' (Argentina)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Pablo Trapero]]\n** ''[[The Club (2015 film)|El Club]]'' (Chile)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Pablo Larra\u00edn]]\n** ''[[A Wolf at the Door (film)|O Lobo Atr\u00e1s da Porta]]'' (Brazil)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Fernando Coimbra]]\n** ''[[Truman (2015 film)|Truman]]'' (Spain)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Cesc Gay]]\n|  style=\"vertical-align:top; width:50%;\"|\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best First Feature Film}}\n* '''''[[600 Miles|600 Millas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 [[Gabriel Ripstein]]'''\n** ''[[El Jerem\u00edas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Anwar Safa\n** ''[[Gloria (2014 film)|Gloria]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Christian Keller\n** ''Hilda''&nbsp;\u2013 Andr\u00e9s Clariond Rangel\n** ''[[The Thin Yellow Line|La Delgada L\u00ednea Amarilla]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Celso Garc\u00eda\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Documentary Feature}}\n* '''''El Hombre Que Vio Demasiado''&nbsp;\u2013 Trisha Ziff'''\n** ''El Paso''&nbsp;\u2013 Everardo Gonz\u00e1lez\n** ''Los Reyes del Pueblo Que No Existe''&nbsp;\u2013 Betzab\u00e9 Garc\u00eda\n** ''Made in Bangkok''&nbsp;\u2013 Flavio Florencio\n** ''Tiempo Suspendido''&nbsp;\u2013 Natalia Bruschtein\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Documentary Short Subject}}\n* '''''Ausencias''&nbsp;\u2013 [[Tatiana Huezo]]'''\n** ''El Buzo''&nbsp;\u2013 Esteban Arrangoiz\n** ''Muchacho en la barra se masturba con rabia y osad\u00eda''&nbsp;\u2013 [[Juli\u00e1n Hern\u00e1ndez (filmmaker)|Juli\u00e1n Hern\u00e1ndez]]\n** ''Por los Caminos del Sur''&nbsp;\u2013 Jorge Luis Linares\n** ''Tob\u00edas''&nbsp;\u2013 Francisca D'Acosta\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Animated Feature Film}}\n* '''''La Incre\u00edble Historia del Ni\u00f1o de Piedra''&nbsp;\u2013 Miguel \u00c1ngel Uriegas, Miguel Bonilla, Jaime Romand\u00eda and Pablo Aldrete'''\n** ''[[El Americano: The Movie]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Ricardo Arnaiz and [[Mike Kunkel]]\n** ''[[Un gallo con muchos huevos|Un Gallo con Muchos Huevos]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Gabriel Riva Palacio and Rodolfo Riva Palacio\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Animated Short}}\n* '''''Zimbo''&nbsp;\u2013 Juan Jos\u00e9 Medina and Rita Basulto'''\n** ''Conejo en la Luna''&nbsp;\u2013 Melissa Ballesteros\n** ''El \u00faltimo jaguar''&nbsp;\u2013 Miguel Anaya\n** ''Los Ases del Corral''&nbsp;\u2013 Irving Sevilla\n** ''Tictact\u00f3polis''&nbsp;\u2013 Jos\u00e9 Sierra\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Original Score}}\n* '''''El Hombre Que Vio Demasiado''&nbsp;\u2013 Jacobo Lieberman'''\n** ''[[Gloria (2014 film)|Gloria]]''&nbsp;\u2013 [[Lorne Balfe]]\n** ''[[The Thin Yellow Line|La Delgada L\u00ednea Amarilla]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Daniel Guillermo Zlotnik\n** ''[[The Chosen Ones (2015 film)|Las Elegidas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Carlo Ayhll\u00f3n\n** ''[[El M\u00e1s Buscado|Mexican Gangster: La Leyenda del Charro Misterioso]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Andr\u00e9s S\u00e1nchez Maher\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Live Action Short}}\n* '''''Tr\u00e9mulo''&nbsp;\u2013 Roberto Fiesco'''\n** ''3 Variaciones de Ofelia''&nbsp;\u2013 Paulo C\u00e9sar Riqu\u00e9\n** ''24\u00b0 51\u2019 Latitud Norte''&nbsp;\u2013 Carlos Lenin\n** ''Esclava''&nbsp;\u2013 [[Amat Escalante]]\n** ''La Teta de Botero''&nbsp;\u2013 Humberto Busto\n** ''Malva''&nbsp;\u2013 Lucero S\u00e1nchez\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Sound}}\n* '''''[[Gloria (2014 film)|Gloria]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Mat\u00edas Barberis, Jaime Baksht and Michelle Couttolenc'''\n** ''[[600 Miles|600 Millas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Alejandro de Icaza and Federico Gonz\u00e1lez Jord\u00e1n\n** ''[[The Thin Yellow Line|La Delgada L\u00ednea Amarilla]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Sergio D\u00edaz, Jaime Baksht and Gabriel Coll\n** ''[[The Chosen Ones (2015 film)|Las Elegidas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Alejandro de Icaza and Pablo Tamez\n** ''[[Un Monstruo de Mil Cabezas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Alejandro de Icaza and Axel Mu\u00f1oz\n| vali