 Ortega-Lee]]&nbsp;\u2013 ''Ella es Ramona'' as Ramona\n** Tatiana del Real&nbsp;\u2013 ''[[Gloria (2014 film)|Gloria]]'' as [[Mary Boquitas|Mar\u00eda Raquenel Portillo]]\n|-\n|  style=\"vertical-align:top; width:50%;\"|\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Original Screenplay}}\n* '''''[[The Chosen Ones (2015 film)|Las Elegidas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 [[David Pablos]]'''\n** ''[[600 Miles|600 Millas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 [[Gabriel Ripstein]] and [[Issa L\u00f3pez]]\n** ''[[Gloria (2014 film)|Gloria]]''&nbsp;\u2013 [[Sabina Berman]]\n** ''[[El Jerem\u00edas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Ana Sof\u00eda Clerici\n** ''[[The Thin Yellow Line|La Delgada L\u00ednea Amarilla]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Celso Garc\u00eda\n|  style=\"vertical-align:top; width:50%;\"|\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Adapted Screenplay}}\n* '''''[[Un Monstruo de Mil Cabezas]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Lauro Santullo from her novel'''\n** ''[[Sand Dollars (film)|D\u00f3lares de Arena]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Israel C\u00e1rdenas and Laura Amelia Guzm\u00e1n from the novel ''Les Dollars des Sables'' by [[Jean-No\u00ebl Pancrazi]]\n** ''La Extinci\u00f3n de los Dinosaurios''&nbsp;\u2013 Luis Ayhll\u00f3n from his play\n** ''Hilda''&nbsp;\u2013 Andr\u00e9s Clariound Rangel from the play ''Hilda'' by [[Marie NDiaye]]\n** ''[[Yo (film)|Yo]]''&nbsp;\u2013 Mat\u00edas Meyer and Alexandre Auger from the short story ''Histoire du pied et autres fantaisies'' by [[J. M. G. Le Cl\u00e9zio]]\n|-\n|  style=\"vertical-align:top; width:50%;\"|\n{{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Iberoamerican Film}}\n* '''''[[Embrace of the Serpent|El Abrazo de la Serpiente]]'' (Colombia)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Ciro Guerra]]'''\n** ''[[The Clan (2015 film)|El Clan]]'' (Argentina)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Pablo Trapero]]\n** ''[[The Club (2015 film)|El Club]]'' (Chile)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Pablo Larra\u00edn]]\n** ''[[A Wolf at the Door (film)|O Lobo Atr\u00e1s da Porta]]'' (Brazil)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Fernando Coimbra]]\n** ''[[Truman (2015 film)|Truman]]'' (Spain)&nbsp;\u2013 [[Cesc Gay]]\n|  style=\"vertical-align:top; width:50